headline: Las Vegas Sands: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: LAS VEGAS (AP) — Las Vegas Sands Corp. LVS) on Wednesday reported fourth-quarter profit of $395 million. The Las Vegas-based company said it had profit of 58 cents per share.
